{
  "videoId": "UZqzsAsoAlo",
  "sceneNum": 4,
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "t": 0.0,
      "end": 10.6,
      "text": "Superheroes, including Frozone, Mr. Incredible, and Elastigirl, caused further damage to the"
    },
    {
      "t": 10.6,
      "end": 11.6,
      "text": "city."
    },
    {
      "t": 11.6,
      "end": 13.56,
      "text": "The Underminer remains at large."
    },
    {
      "t": 13.56,
      "end": 14.88,
      "text": "We didn't start this fight!"
    },
    {
      "t": 14.88,
      "end": 16.24,
      "text": "Well, you didn't finish it either!"
    },
    {
      "t": 16.24,
      "end": 18.8,
      "text": "Did you stop the Underminer from inflicting more damage?"
    },
    {
      "t": 18.8,
      "end": 19.8,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "t": 19.8,
      "end": 21.44,
      "text": "Did you stop him from robbing the banks?"
    },
    {
      "t": 21.44,
      "end": 22.44,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "t": 22.44,
      "end": 23.44,
      "text": "Did you catch him?"
    },
    {
      "t": 23.44,
      "end": 24.44,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "t": 24.44,
      "end": 25.44,
      "text": "The banks were insured."
    },
    {
      "t": 25.44,
      "end": 28.04,
      "text": "We have infrastructure in place to deal with these matters."
    },
    {
      "t": 28.04,
      "end": 32.84,
      "text": "If you had simply done nothing, everything would now be proceeding in an orderly fashion."
    },
    {
      "t": 32.84,
      "end": 35.52,
      "text": "You'd have preferred we do nothing?"
    },
    {
      "t": 35.52,
      "end": 41.04,
      "text": "Without a doubt."
    },
    {
      "t": 41.04,
      "end": 42.04,
      "text": "You weren't much help."
    },
    {
      "t": 42.04,
      "end": 44.68,
      "text": "You want out of the hole?"
    },
    {
      "t": 44.68,
      "end": 47.72,
      "text": "First you gotta put down the shovel."
    },
    {
      "t": 47.72,
      "end": 52.72,
      "text": "Well, that went poorly."
    },
    {
      "t": 52.72,
      "end": 60.04,
      "text": "Dad, this is probably not the best time to tell you about this, but something else happened"
    },
    {
      "t": 60.04,
      "end": 61.04,
      "text": "today."
    },
    {
      "t": 61.04,
      "end": 62.92,
      "text": "With a kid."
    },
    {
      "t": 62.92,
      "end": 66.92,
      "text": "And my mask."
    },
    {
      "t": 66.92,
      "end": 82.68,
      "text": "Oh, hey, Rick, Violet thinks a friend of hers, a kid named Tony, he might have seen her."
    },
    {
      "t": 82.68,
      "end": 83.68,
      "text": "I've seen her in the outfit."
    },
    {
      "t": 83.68,
      "end": 84.68,
      "text": "Without her mask."
    },
    {
      "t": 84.68,
      "end": 85.68,
      "text": "Talkative type?"
    },
    {
      "t": 85.68,
      "end": 86.68,
      "text": "Don't know."
    },
    {
      "t": 86.68,
      "end": 87.68,
      "text": "Last name is Reitinger."
    },
    {
      "t": 87.68,
      "end": 88.68,
      "text": "Tony Reitinger."
    },
    {
      "t": 88.68,
      "end": 89.68,
      "text": "I'll check it out."
    },
    {
      "t": 89.68,
      "end": 90.68,
      "text": "Bob, Ellen, a word if you don't mind."
    },
    {
      "t": 90.68,
      "end": 91.68,
      "text": "The program's been shut down."
    },
    {
      "t": 91.68,
      "end": 92.68,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "t": 92.68,
      "end": 93.68,
      "text": "Politicians don't understand people who do good simply because it's right."
    },
    {
      "t": 93.68,
      "end": 94.68,
      "text": "It makes them nervous."
    },
    {
      "t": 94.68,
      "end": 95.68,
      "text": "They've been gunning for supers for years."
    },
    {
      "t": 95.68,
      "end": 96.68,
      "text": "Today was all they needed."
    },
    {
      "t": 97.68,
      "end": 98.68,
      "text": "Anyway, I'm done."
    },
    {
      "t": 98.68,
      "end": 99.68,
      "text": "I'm afraid two more weeks in the motel is the best I can do for you."
    },
    {
      "t": 99.68,
      "end": 100.68,
      "text": "It ain't much."
    },
    {
      "t": 100.68,
      "end": 101.68,
      "text": "You've done plenty, Rick."
    },
    {
      "t": 101.68,
      "end": 102.68,
      "text": "We won't forget."
    },
    {
      "t": 102.68,
      "end": 103.68,
      "text": "Well, it has been a great honor working with you."
    },
    {
      "t": 103.68,
      "end": 104.68,
      "text": "I'll see you later."
    },
    {
      "t": 104.68,
      "end": 105.68,
      "text": "Bye."
